 import { Doughnut } from 'react-chartjs-2';
 
 ChartJS.register(ArcElement, Tooltip, Legend);
 
-export const data = {

-      data: [12, 19, 3, 5, 2, 3],

-        'rgba(255, 99, 132, 0.2)',
-        'rgba(54, 162, 235, 0.2)',
-        'rgba(255, 206, 86, 0.2)',
-        'rgba(75, 192, 192, 0.2)',
-        'rgba(153, 102, 255, 0.2)',
-        'rgba(255, 159, 64, 0.2)',
-      ],
-      borderColor: [
-        'rgba(255, 99, 132, 1)',
-        'rgba(54, 162, 235, 1)',
-        'rgba(255, 206, 86, 1)',
-        'rgba(75, 192, 192, 1)',
-        'rgba(153, 102, 255, 1)',
-        'rgba(255, 159, 64, 1)',
-      ],
-      borderWidth: 1,
-    },
-  ],
-};
 
+
 export function DoughnutChart() {
   return <Doughnut data={data} />;
 }
